Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.63,0:04:17.09,insert_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Welcome to Rock'n Roll Fight
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.09,0:04:18.92,insert_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I'm just a Rock'n Roll MAN
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.05,0:04:21.32,insert_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}We're just a Rock'n Roll BAND
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.40,0:04:27.75,insert_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}俺達は道なりに　走り続けて来た
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.79,0:04:33.06,insert_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}標識だらけの道を　とばし続けていく
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.09,0:04:38.38,insert_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}幾つもの町を抜け　歌い続けて来た
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.64,0:04:43.78,insert_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}腑抜け野郎共を　煽り続けていく
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.06,0:04:50.80,insert_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}長い長い冬が溶けても 風が吹く
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.93,0:04:55.88,insert_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}今も今も激しく風が吹く
